title: Counter-Strike 1.5 Full + PODBot
description:
Counter-Strike 1.5 Full Install + BOTS

Included is the WON2 Compatibility to play online as well as an updated 1.1.1.2 patch which fixes bugs, also included are bots from PODBot to add bots start a new game and press the '=' key to add them.

Metamod and Amxmod plugins will work but not Amxmodx, so be aware.

Remember to seed once you have finished downloading.
